FILO.CLASSIC_DESCRIPTION: Filo is a powerful multipurpose Discord bot. Customizable, multiple languages, report, logging, welcomes and farewells, member counter, anti-invites, auto-mod, anti-evasion. +190 commands.
FILO.DESCRIPTION: Filo 是一個功能強大且多用途的 Discord 機器人，自 2019 年以來就一直努力不懈的在 Discord 伺服器上服務。她擁有廣泛的管理和審核模塊，讓您工作更輕鬆。

REPORTS.TITLE: Reports
REPORTS.DESCRIPTION: Enhance the experience and professionalize your server moderation by allowing users to report inappropriate behavior!

LOGGING.TITLE: Logging
LOGGING.DESCRIPTION: Log all actions performed by users in your server to a channel, allowing you to easily review and filter them!

ANTI_INVITES.TITLE: Anti Invites
ANTI_INVITES.DESCRIPTION: Prevent users from sending invites from your servers to yours by automatically sanctioning them!

ANTI_SPAM.TITLE: Anti Spam
ANTI_SPAM.DESCRIPTION: Tired of spammers? Are your moderators not enough? Let Filo deal with this class of users and have some tea in the meantime!

ANTI_BAD_WORDS.TITLE: Anti Bad Words
ANTI_BAD_WORDS.DESCRIPTION: Prevent users from using bad words in their messages... Nobody likes having to read those words!

ANTI_SCAM_LINKS.TITLE: Anti Scam Links
ANTI_SCAM_LINKS.DESCRIPTION: Scammers, what tiresome people... Now Filo can help you fight these types of people!

AUTO_MODERATION.TITLE: Auto Moderation
AUTO_MODERATION.DESCRIPTION: Don't allow conflicting users to exist on your server, this can negatively affect the experience of legitimate users!

ANTI_EVASION.TITLE: Anti Evasion
ANTI_EVASION.DESCRIPTION: Have you muted several users and they have left the server? No problem! Let Filo automatically ban these users!
